    tibble,
    dplyr,
    flextable,
    htmltools,
    knitr,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    rlang,
    stringr,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: 
    bookdown,
    officedown,
    testthat,
    rmarkdown
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
URL: https://montesmariana.github.io/glossr/, https://github.com/montesmariana/glossr
